{"tid":838048,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳若希爆曾被老公背叛","createTime":"2018-09-26T23:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T10:09:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c8534295a173cbdb0f1b6cb63e77a2b998ae8c47","tid":838048,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T23:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180927/large/27ec3p22e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180927%2Flarge%2F27ec3p22e.jpg&h=3aff9724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳若希昨日到新城宣傳新歌《為何你要背叛我》，歌曲講述兩人感情之間需要坦承而做到互相信任。她憶述當初發現老公於感情上背叛自己時，她說：「我好似癲咗，嗰時拍緊嘢，喺一廠出面不停打電話，因為對段感情越認真，就越對背叛嘅事上心。」<br />\n之前在另一段感情上亦遇到背叛，吳若希笑說：「對方已經消失天地之間，希望佢學習到一啲嘢以後生生性性。」至於當初怎樣重建對丈夫信任，她說：「我都想知，可能陀BB時我幾無理取鬧，例如朝早六點要食炒飯，唔鍾意間新屋，直情冇住就搬去第二間，嗰一下就覺得可以付託畀佢。"},{"pid":"29213d1a1cb32a9fcf974f4f0897ef3ed782252d","tid":838048,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T23:23:20.000Z","msg":"估唔到何生係d咁既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa09b4cf1a3a2b4fe75b42365a63eab312c4b8d0","tid":838048,"uid":8572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T23:23:21.000Z","msg":"因為何生食左hana?"},{"pid":"e49c2b8f2421255430c04f215441c57a0bcec4a5","tid":838048,"uid":144464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T23:33:49.000Z","msg":"點解嘅"},{"pid":"9e151b23a409107a6e866db788dcb3588d643ae2","tid":838048,"uid":62384,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T23:41:13.000Z","msg":"睇你好得幾撚耐"},{"pid":"7bd3c1a9e07703bbb51f6df85a49185872f01f82","tid":838048,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T23:48:56.000Z","msg":"扮慘谷人氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea14639a4ffe29f37189a77934f4c54620e324c","tid":838048,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r